divs: Sighting Detailsas we were in our gym at the apartments we live at it was a sunny clear day out i was looking outside of the window when i saw a bright shining silver oblong shape thing in the sky it was just sitting there in the air as i watch it it started to move slowly across the sky very slow i thought it was a plane but the it when very fast and disappeared out of sight. it has shapes to the structure. i can draw it and send it to you in a few days.
Summary: saw in out a window of our gym
